OL,4,CWrexham councillor defends Panama
OL,5,C'working holiday'
OL,6, Wrexham council's lead member for
OL,7, children's services has been criticised
OL,8, for working remotely from Central
OL,9, America while the department faces
OL,10, "significant concerns".
OL,12,FAndrew Atkinson, who gets an allowance
OL,13,Fof #30,450, told the Local Democracy
OL,14,FReporting Service he is on a "working
OL,15,Fholiday" in Panama.
OL,17,FWrexham's children's services are under
OL,18,Fscrutiny from Care Inspectorate Wales.
OL,20,FWrexham council said Mr Atkinson was
OL,21,Fstill attending meetings "remotely".
